There's nowhere we can hide,

190
00:18:03,280 --> 00:18:07,353
But we can't delay our life
for later.

191
00:18:09,120 --> 00:18:14,638
There's nowhere we can hide,
but somewhere there...

192
00:18:15,520 --> 00:18:20,116
there's someone in the rain
looking for you!

193
00:18:22,960 --> 00:18:28,193
The fearful peals of thunder
from dusk till dawn...

194
00:18:29,520 --> 00:18:34,036
Bad weather is the atonement
for the people's sins.

195
00:18:35,840 --> 00:18:40,391
Not angina, not common cold.
It is a worse disaster.

196
