- Really?

239
00:21:49,760 --> 00:21:51,159
So it is.

240
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:56,595
But I don't understand,
what for?

241
00:21:57,640 --> 00:22:00,996
Excellent. A most convenient
thing to transport buys!

242
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:03,039
You may go now.

243
00:22:18,880 --> 00:22:19,995
Hey!

244
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:25,429
May I ask, why you call me
Mister Hey, Mary Poppins?

245
00:22:26,280 --> 00:22:28,999
Mister Hey! I like that!
Mister Hey!

246
00:22:29,360 --> 00:22:31,476
He starts all his songs with
a "Hey"!

247
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:33,916
Well of course it's Mister Hey!
How do you do, Mister Hey!

248
00:22:34,200 --> 00:22:36,634
I don't like the way you
speak to your uncle.

249
00:22:36,920 --> 00:22:40,833
Don't forget to turn off the gas
under the big pan,..

250
00:22:41,280 --> 00:22:43,191
Mister Hey.

251
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:46,668
- Mrs. Lark, I beg you!
- My God! My boy got lost again!

252
00:22:47,280 --> 00:22:50,192
We must call the police
and the fire brigade!

253
00:22:50,600 --> 00:22:52,750
Poor, poor Mrs. Lark.

254
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:58,435
There he is! Near admiral
Boom's place!

255
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:03,391
My God, Edward! My little doggy!
Edward!

256
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:08,637
Oh, no! This horrible shaggy
mongrel again!

257
00:23:08,960 --> 00:23:12,635
Go away! Go away! Edward,
come home this very minute!

258
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:18,713
To run away all alone, without a
coat! I am very displeased.

259
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:21,912
You have no heart for me,
Edward! Come home!

260
00:23:22,560 --> 00:23:25,950
He says he is not coming home.

261
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:32,073
And how do you know what my dog
is saying, may I ask?

262
00:23:32,960 --> 00:23:34,757
He is going home this instant.

263
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:39,111
He won't go without his friend.

264
00:23:41,280 --> 00:23:47,355
How can he even think that I
will let in this shaggy animal?

265
00:23:47,920 --> 00:23:51,356
- He says the issue is closed.
- What?!

266
00:23:52,160 --> 00:23:59,191
That - after everything I've
done for you, Edward?

267
00:24:01,520 --> 00:24:06,799
All right, all right, let it be
on your terms. But from now on

268
00:24:07,640 --> 00:24:10,598
... my heart is broken forever.
Forever!

269
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:13,833
So it's decided.

270
00:24:15,160 --> 00:24:20,154
I will name the dog Shaggy
or Boy.

271
00:24:22,160 --> 00:24:26,119
No, his name is Bartholomew.
And no other name will do.

272
00:24:26,440 --> 00:24:28,431
Bartholomew?!

273
00:24:29,280 --> 00:24:31,236
That's all I need.

274
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:35,911
What else does he say?

275
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:40,557
He says he will come back
on one condition...

276
00:24:41,160 --> 00:24:44,675
... That you will never make
him wear his coat.

277
00:24:46,320 --> 00:24:49,118
- It's his final word.
- Very well..

278
00:24:49,440 --> 00:24:53,558
But if you catch cold and start
sneezing, It will be your fault!

279
00:24:59,040 --> 00:25:01,031
Do come in!

280
00:25:01,560 --> 00:25:04,552
What a charming lady
moved to our neighborhood.

281
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:07,992
2 pounds of the best sausages,
and quick. We're in a hurry.

282
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:12,392
In a hurry? What a pity.

283
00:25:13,360 --> 00:25:14,713
What a pity!

284
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:20,157
I was hoping you would stay a
while, and we will chat a bit.

285
00:25:20,440 --> 00:25:22,032
How about that?

286
00:25:22,640 --> 00:25:26,553
You know, us butchers like
company.

287
00:25:29,520 --> 00:25:31,636
What is the young lady
doing tonight?

288
00:25:37,240 --> 00:25:41,279
2 pounds, you said? La-la!

289
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:44,670
The very best I have,
of course!

290
00:25:47,800 --> 00:25:50,917
I'm at your service! I'm at
your service!

291
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:06,792
Yes! Yes! Since you're
in a hurry,

292
00:26:07,280 --> 00:26:09,236
... then by all means.
For you, of course,

