Oh, what nasty weather!

298
00:26:36,040 --> 00:26:39,476
Oh, that Eastern wind!

299
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:45,075
Looks like there will be no
summer,

300
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:54,835
... and I come to think of it,
there wasn't any.

301
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:07,674
I wouldn't say you look very
healthy either.

302
00:27:09,760 --> 00:27:13,673
