... surprising!

304
00:27:23,320 --> 00:27:25,515
I heard something...

305
00:27:26,040 --> 00:27:29,316
... from the man in the
butcher's shop.

306
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:44,270
Who - from the hair-pin to the
safety-pin,

307
00:27:45,360 --> 00:27:47,590
From the hat down to the shoes...

308
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:50,159
Is sheer elegance?

309
00:27:50,480 --> 00:27:55,190
They're all crazy about me:
a gray-haired gentlemen

310
00:27:56,240 --> 00:27:58,231
And a young boy.

311
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:01,470
I come out to the crossing

312
00:28:02,560 --> 00:28:04,471
With a nonchalant air,

313
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:09,834
